invalid type: string "Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita, 2023 ‚Äî Section 304: Snatching\n\nKeywords: snatching, chain snatching, mobile snatching, theft with force, sudden seizure\n\nWhoever commits theft, with the intent to cause hurt or fear of hurt to any person, by suddenly or quickly or forcibly seizing or securing or grabbing from any person any moveable property, is said to commit snatching.\n\nˇˇˇˇ